# Password Manager
Password manager providing option to store and add password.
Passwords are stored in json file using libsodium for encryption and hashing.

![Password Manager Screenshot](password_manager.png)
A modern C++ application providing simple GUI using ImGui.

## Table of Contents
- [Description](#description)
- [Features](#features)
- [License](#license)
- [Installation](#installation)

## Description
This is an application with a simple graphical user interface and the ability to store multiple passwords in a secure location if the application is used on a single computer by different family members, teachers or company employees who want to save their passwords without the need for the Internet.

## Features
- Registration or login
- Unlocking stored passwords with a special key
- Storing your password securely

